Package utils

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlertBox
    Contains methods used for displaying AlertBoxes to the user in different scenarios.
    DataAccessCreate
    Contains the methods for Creating new Appointments and Customers and adding them to the Database.
    DataAccessDelete
    Contains the methods for Deleting the Customer or Appointment from the Database.
    DataAccessRead
    Contains the methods for fetching data from the Database into ObservableLists, and interacting with the ObservableLists.
    DataAccessUpdate
    Contains the methods for updating rows in the Database.
    DBConnection
    Contains the methods for connecting to the Database.
    DBQuery
    Contains the PreparedStatement methods for interacting with the Database.
    Language
    Contains methods for translating text for the Login screen.
    TimeUtility
    Contains methods for converting and formatting time and timestamps.
